Dáte si koláč?

87
00:08:15,080 --> 00:08:16,560
Koláč?

88
00:08:19,520 --> 00:08:20,960
Ako to ide?

89
00:08:22,260 --> 00:08:23,280
Zle.

90
00:08:23,540 --> 00:08:25,300
Dáte si?

91
