95
00:08:47,480 --> 00:08:49,180
Nebudeme mať u neho problém?

96
00:08:49,240 --> 00:08:51,760
Už som s ním hovoril, dobre?

97
00:08:51,760 --> 00:08:53,360
Nebude žiaden problém.

98
00:08:53,580 --> 00:08:54,580
Dobre.

99
00:08:54,960 --> 00:08:57,320
Dáte si koláč?

100
00:08:57,320 --> 00:08:59,560
Výborný čokoládový koláč za 40 Bahtov.

101
00:08:59,620 --> 00:09:00,640
Výborný.

102
00:09:04,580 --> 00:09:06,200
Myslíš si, že niečo predáme?

103
00:09:06,200 --> 00:09:09,000
Už tu stojím asi hodinu,
no nikto to nechce.

104
00:09:09,260 --> 00:09:11,240
Možno vyzeráme príliš obyčajne.

105
00:09:22,680 --> 00:09:23,980
Neviem.

106
00:09:23,980 --> 00:09:25,160
Hneď sa vrátim.

107
00:09:28,440 --> 00:09:30,120
Myslíš si, že to zaberie?

108
00:09:30,120 --> 00:09:31,600
Ver mi.

109
00:09:32,420 --> 00:09:34,140
Toto nie je môj štýl.

110
00:09:34,140 --> 00:09:36,080
Nechcem tie koláče ťahať naspäť domov.

111
00:09:37,540 --> 00:09:38,680
Dobre.

112
00:09:38,680 --> 00:09:39,800
Pripravený?

113
00:09:39,800 --> 00:09:40,800
Nasleduj ma.

114
00:09:40,800 --> 00:09:41,760
Dobre.

115
00:09:42,900 --> 00:09:45,720
Dáte si koláč?
Iba 40 Bahtov!

116
00:09:46,280 --> 00:09:48,160
Sú vynikajúce!

117
00:09:50,700 --> 00:09:52,120
40 Bahtov.

118
00:09:52,120 --> 00:09:53,440
Môžem vás vyfotiť?

119
00:09:53,440 --> 00:09:54,680
Áno.

120
00:10:00,920 --> 00:10:02,480
Máte našu fotku.

121
00:10:02,480 --> 00:10:04,180
Chceli by ste aj náš koláč?

122
00:10:05,200 --> 00:10:06,440
Koľko kúskov?

123
00:10:06,660 --> 00:10:08,660
Dva?
Dobre.

124
00:10:08,720 --> 00:10:10,660
A čo štyri?

125
00:10:13,600 --> 00:10:15,240
Štyri kúsky za 160 Bahtov.

126
00:10:16,440 --> 00:10:18,140
Ďakujeme.

127
00:10:19,340 --> 00:10:21,200
Funguje to.

128
00:10:21,200 --> 00:10:22,140
Hovoril som ti.

129
00:10:23,080 --> 00:10:26,360
Koláč!
Iba za 40 Bahtov.

130
00:10:26,520 --> 00:10:27,840
40 Bahtov.

131
00:10:27,840 --> 00:10:30,300
Mohli by ste mi dať každý po 10 Bahtov, pán Zajačik?

132
00:10:30,440 --> 00:10:31,880
Manow.

133
00:10:32,620 --> 00:10:34,320
Začínaš s nami vyjednávať?

134
00:10:34,320 --> 00:10:36,480
Naozaj ich chceš?
Už ma to tu unavuje.

135
00:10:36,480 --> 00:10:37,440
Kamoš.

136
00:10:37,600 --> 00:10:39,200
Myslíš to vážne?

137
00:10:39,260 --> 00:10:40,780
Naozaj si ich zoberiem.

138
00:10:40,820 --> 00:10:41,880
Dobre!

139
00:10:41,880 --> 00:10:45,060
Chcem vedieť,
čo si myslíš o mojom pečení.

140
00:10:46,060 --> 00:10:48,200
Upiekol si ich?

141
00:10:48,280 --> 00:10:49,280
Áno.

142
00:10:53,380 --> 00:10:54,940
Mork, Rain.

143
00:10:55,220 --> 00:11:00,480
Chcem sa vám poďakovať za ten deň.

144
00:11:00,480 --> 00:11:03,400
Nemáš zač.
Každý by ti pomohol.

145
00:11:03,760 --> 00:11:05,340
Nemysli na to.

146
00:11:07,640 --> 00:11:09,540
Je mi to ľúto.

147
00:11:10,060 --> 00:11:12,420
Skončili ste kvôli mne na polícií.

148
00:11:12,420 --> 00:11:14,920
A čo keby si si kúpila celý koláč?

149
00:11:16,860 --> 00:11:18,120
Žartujem.

150
00:11:18,120 --> 00:11:20,600
Čoskoro si ho aj tak niekto kúpi.

151
00:11:21,540 --> 00:11:22,960
Daj si jeden.

152
00:11:23,620 --> 00:11:25,260
Ďakujem.

153
00:11:28,100 --> 00:11:29,960
Vypredajme ich.

154
00:11:29,960 --> 00:11:31,660
Dáte si niekto koláč?
Koláč vyrobený dvoma zajačikmi.

155
00:11:33,260 --> 00:11:34,900
Dáte si koláč?

156
00:11:35,380 --> 00:11:36,860
Koláč.

157
00:11:39,620 --> 00:11:41,140
Hej.

158
00:11:41,760 --> 00:11:42,800
Mám nápad.

159
00:11:43,040 --> 00:11:44,720
Postráž mi to.

160
00:11:48,260 --> 00:11:52,260
Výborné koláče vyrobené roztomilými chlapcami!

161
00:11:52,260 --> 00:11:53,640
Jeden kúsok za 40 Bahtov!

162
00:11:53,680 --> 00:11:55,960
Kúpte si ich predtým,
ako sa vypredajú!

163
00:11:55,960 --> 00:11:57,800
Ochutnajte!

164
00:11:58,880 --> 00:12:01,800
Sú výborné.

165
00:12:02,040 --> 00:12:04,360
Poďte si dať koláč!

166
00:12:05,680 --> 00:12:07,880
Môžete sa s nimi aj vyfotiť.

167
00:12:08,680 --> 00:12:10,320
Iba 40 Bahtov za kúsok!

168
00:12:10,320 --> 00:12:14,080
Poďte si pre koláč!

169
00:12:14,880 --> 00:12:16,360
Môžete sa s nimi aj vyfotiť.

170
00:12:16,360 --> 00:12:18,420
Poďte!

171
00:12:18,420 --> 00:12:20,100
Sú výborné!

172
00:12:43,520 --> 00:12:44,820
Hej.

173
00:12:44,980 --> 00:12:47,340
Prišiel si neskôr, ako obvykle.

174
00:12:47,380 --> 00:12:49,800
Pred svojim poúčaním sa ma spýtaj,
čo som robil.

175
00:12:50,060 --> 00:12:51,180
Čo si robil?

176
00:12:51,600 --> 00:12:56,260
Išiel som predať naše koláče,
ktorým končí spotreba.

177
00:12:57,540 --> 00:12:58,960
Mork mi pomohol.

178
00:12:59,600 --> 00:13:01,240
Vypredali sme ich.

179
00:13:03,480 --> 00:13:04,660
Mork?

180
00:13:05,920 --> 00:13:07,420
Vie obchodovať?

181
00:13:07,860 --> 00:13:09,080
Neviem si to predstaviť.

182
00:13:10,400 --> 00:13:12,000
Prestaň.

183
00:13:12,360 --> 00:13:14,920
Je to dobrý predajca.

184
00:13:15,300 --> 00:13:18,200
Obľúbilo si ho niekoľko dievčat.

185
00:13:19,580 --> 00:13:20,580
Dobre.

186
00:13:21,120 --> 00:13:22,840
Dúfam, že mi rýchlo vráti tie peniaze.

187
00:13:23,300 --> 00:13:25,180
Okrem toho, zobral si mi koláče.
Kúp mi nové.

188
00:13:25,880 --> 00:13:27,440
Som tvoj brat.

189
00:13:27,480 --> 00:13:28,760
No a?

190
00:13:32,980 --> 00:13:34,760
Strhnem ti tie peniaze z výplaty.

191
00:13:34,760 --> 00:13:36,360
Nie, to nerob.

192
00:13:36,360 --> 00:13:38,420
Prečo by si to robil?

193
00:13:38,420 --> 00:13:40,760
Pretože mi tie peniaze z predaja nedáš.

194
00:13:43,100 --> 00:13:44,440
Super.

195
00:13:44,440 --> 00:13:45,440
Choď.

196
00:13:46,360 --> 00:13:48,360
Zase sa hráš?

197
00:13:49,000 --> 00:13:51,160
Zostáva ti päť minút.

198
00:13:51,460 --> 00:13:53,660
Po kontrole tvojej úlohy budeme opäť pokračovať.

199
00:13:54,880 --> 00:13:55,880
Dobre?

200
00:13:56,940 --> 00:14:01,340
Vieš o tom,
že som RoV Pro?

201
00:14:01,960 --> 00:14:04,180
Už tri sezóny po sebe si držím svoje miesto.

202
00:14:05,560 --> 00:14:08,700
Mal by si aj ty začať hrať túto hru.

203
00:14:10,400 --> 00:14:11,500
Nie.

204
00:14:11,500 --> 00:14:13,980
Mám málo času
a nemienim svoj voľný čas premrhať na hry.

205
00:14:14,620 --> 00:14:16,960
Mal by si to skúsiť.

206
00:14:16,960 --> 00:14:18,580
Mali by sme sa o čom baviť.

207
00:14:25,120 --> 00:14:26,120
Prehral som.

208
00:14:26,900 --> 00:14:29,100
Si ako iný človek,
keď nie si doma.

209
00:14:32,280 --> 00:14:34,860
Bývaš iba s otcom?

210
00:14:36,020 --> 00:14:37,080
Áno.

211
00:14:37,960 --> 00:14:39,840
Ale nevídam sa s ním často.

212
00:14:41,360 --> 00:14:42,800
A ani nechcem.

213
00:14:43,840 --> 00:14:45,520
Idem za ním iba keď chcem peniaze.

214
00:14:47,920 --> 00:14:50,720
Nevedel som,
že je taký prísny.

215
00:14:53,540 --> 00:14:57,080
Nikdy taký nebol,
keď bola mama ešte s nami.

216
00:14:58,080 --> 00:15:03,140
Tvoja mama...

217
00:15:03,840 --> 00:15:05,220
je preč?

218
00:15:05,580 --> 00:15:06,940
Žije.

219
00:15:08,240 --> 00:15:10,160
Ale našla si nového chlapa.

220
00:15:12,240 --> 00:15:14,140
Preto je otec taký nahnevaný.

221
00:15:17,300 --> 00:15:19,840
Vyzerá veľmi nahnevane.

222
00:15:20,520 --> 00:15:21,600
Áno.

223
00:15:24,720 --> 00:15:26,460
Prepáč, že sa ťa pýtam také osobné otázky.

224
00:15:27,520 --> 00:15:28,780
To nevadí.

225
00:15:29,460 --> 00:15:32,360
Ľudia sa väčšinou o tom so mnou nebavia.

226
00:15:37,680 --> 00:15:40,420
Zaujímaš sa o mňa?

227
00:15:42,900 --> 00:15:45,260
Vrátime sa k tebe domov?

228
00:15:51,400 --> 00:15:54,420
Do ďalšej hodiny si urob všetky úlohy.

229
00:15:54,420 --> 00:15:55,940
Nemusíš na mňa čakať.

230
00:15:55,940 --> 00:15:57,480
Dobre.

231
00:15:57,480 --> 00:15:58,980
A ty by si mal vyskúšať RoV.

232
00:16:09,920 --> 00:16:11,620
Hej, tak ako?

233
00:16:12,240 --> 00:16:14,440
Kde si?
Čo robíš?

234
00:16:16,720 --> 00:16:19,780
Učím.

235
00:16:20,820 --> 00:16:22,080
Nudím sa.

236
00:16:23,100 --> 00:16:26,280
Pamätáš si otcovho kamaráta
z toho stretnutia v tom hoteli?

237
00:16:26,760 --> 00:16:28,080
Áno.

238
00:16:28,600 --> 00:16:30,800
Zase sa ma pýtal na tú stáž.
Je to otravné.

239
00:16:32,460 --> 00:16:35,060
Upokoj sa.

240
00:16:35,760 --> 00:16:37,300
Odišiel som.

241
00:16:38,060 --> 00:16:39,500
Idem za tebou.

242
00:16:40,280 --> 00:16:42,600
Dobre.

243
00:16:44,800 --> 00:16:47,180
Uvidíme sa u Suna.
Už som tam.

244
00:16:52,220 --> 00:16:54,040
Nemal by si sa tak tváriť pred zákazníkmi.

245
00:16:54,120 --> 00:16:55,660
